; brief: C, D shall be able to access accelerometer data under org.md2k        ;this is the same as policy6, but a different implementation

policy-id           6
requester-ids       /org/md2k/C,/org/md2k/D
attribute-filters
{
    allow
    {
        /org/md2k/
        /org/md2k/attribute/sensor/accelerometer ;attribute associated with any/all accelerometer data
    }
}

